&lt;p&gt;An exciting opportunity has arisen for a Band 5 Staff Nurse to join the experienced teams of staff working within the Intermediate Care Community Hospitals at Westbourne Green Community Hospital.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We are looking for a committed, hardworking and caring individual who is forward thinking with strong leadership qualities, who is keen to support new developments and changes taking place within the community setting. You will demonstrate an interest of working with older people.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;All Community Hospitals are nurse led units and are closely supported by the Elderly Care Consultants from Bradford Teaching Hospitals, including the wider multidisciplinary team of Physiotherapists, Occupational Therapists and Social Workers.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;If you want to make a difference, and be given the time to care, enjoy working within a supportive team, be recognized and valued for your hard work and commitment – then come and work with us.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Informal Enquiries to Jackie Crabtree on 01274 322093&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;E-mail: Jacqueline.Crabtree2@bthft.nhs.uk&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Closing Date: 8 November 2020 - (This date may change dependent on the response)&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
